1
00:00:42,167 --> 00:00:45,962
LIKE FLOWERS IN SAND

2
00:00:47,130 --> 00:00:50,675
Ayah akan pergi berlatih. 
Jangan lupa sarapan.

3
00:01:17,452 --> 00:01:22,582
Saat masih kecil, 
orang-orang sering berkata kepadaku,

4
00:01:23,792 --> 00:01:26,169
"Kau pasti kesepian, Du-sik."

5
00:01:26,252 --> 00:01:28,755
"Kau pasti bosan sendirian."

6
00:01:31,591 --> 00:01:35,553
Namun, mereka tak tahu 
apa yang mereka bicarakan.

7
00:01:37,347 --> 00:01:41,518
Aku tak pernah sempat kesepian 
atau merasa bosan saat itu.

8
00:01:46,272 --> 00:01:47,816
- Sakit! 
- Pertama,

9
00:01:47,899 --> 00:01:50,151
ada Kim Baek-du, yang menemaniku

10
00:01:50,235 --> 00:01:52,070
- Tunggu aku! 
- sepanjang hari.

11
00:01:52,153 --> 00:01:53,613
Hei, Oh Du-sik!

12
00:01:53,696 --> 00:01:55,073
- Kau tak… 
- Tak perlu.

13
00:01:55,156 --> 00:01:56,658
Tunggu. Makan ini.

14
00:01:56,741 --> 00:01:57,784
- Tidak. 
- Satu lagi.

15
00:01:57,867 --> 00:01:59,119
Ada Jin-su juga.

16
00:01:59,202 --> 00:02:01,496
- Hei, Baek-du. 
- Jin-su!

17
00:02:01,579 --> 00:02:04,290
Hei, Anak-Anak.

18
00:02:04,374 --> 00:02:07,836
Jangan lupa buku catatan kalian. 
Kalian sudah mengerjakan PR?

19
00:02:07,919 --> 00:02:09,838
- Aku harus pergi. 
- Pegang ini.

20
00:02:09,921 --> 00:02:11,589
Kunyah dengan baik.

21
00:02:11,673 --> 00:02:14,217
Jangan makan yang sudah jatuh ke tanah.

22
00:02:14,300 --> 00:02:16,219
- Baiklah. 
- Tunggu!

23
00:02:16,302 --> 00:02:18,054
Jangan bertengkar dan malas!

24
00:02:19,389 --> 00:02:20,723
Kau seperti anak lelaki.

25
00:02:20,807 --> 00:02:21,724
Kau memang lelaki.

26
00:02:23,935 --> 00:02:25,937
- Ada Seok-hui juga. 
- Sudah kerjakan PR?

27
00:02:26,020 --> 00:02:27,188
Kau lupa soal itu?

28
00:02:27,272 --> 00:02:30,150
Itu mudah bagiku. 
Kujawab banyak pertanyaan.

29
00:02:33,945 --> 00:02:34,904
Apa jawabannya?

30
00:02:35,530 --> 00:02:36,739
Satu.

31
00:02:36,823 --> 00:02:38,533
- Aku seperti nenek. 
- Bukan itu!

32
00:02:39,951 --> 00:02:41,786
Ada juga Mi-ran.

33
00:02:47,584 --> 00:02:48,501
Mi-ran!

34
00:02:51,254 --> 00:02:54,883
Kami selalu bersama.

35
00:03:00,680 --> 00:03:06,519
EPISODE 10, SELAMANYA TERBELIT, 
TAK HENTI TERJALIN

36
00:03:08,271 --> 00:03:09,814
Aku sangat menyukaimu.

37
00:03:11,733 --> 00:03:13,151
Sungguh.

38
00:03:17,488 --> 00:03:19,824
Jadi…

39
00:03:20,575 --> 00:03:23,995
maksudmu

40
00:03:25,163 --> 00:03:26,414
kau…

41
00:03:27,332 --> 00:03:29,000
- menyimpan perasaan itu? 
- Ya.

42
00:03:29,083 --> 00:03:30,752
- Aku menyukaimu. 
- Baiklah.

43
00:03:30,835 --> 00:03:32,545
Berhenti mengatakan itu.

44
00:03:33,421 --> 00:03:34,923
Aku mendengarmu.

45
00:03:37,634 --> 00:03:38,468
Baiklah.

46
00:03:39,552 --> 00:03:40,762
Yang benar saja.

47
00:03:41,846 --> 00:03:44,182
Aku tidak menduga hal ini.

48
00:03:45,725 --> 00:03:48,603
Kau sungguh pandai

49
00:03:49,270 --> 00:03:51,981
membuatku terkejut.

50
00:03:52,482 --> 00:03:53,399
Aku tahu.

51
00:03:53,983 --> 00:03:55,902
Saat menyadari aku menyukaimu,

52
00:03:55,985 --> 00:03:57,612
- aku juga… 
- Sudahlah!

53
00:03:59,697 --> 00:04:03,201
Berhenti berkata kau menyukaiku.

54
00:04:04,619 --> 00:04:07,163
Itu terlalu menggelikan.

55
00:04:12,627 --> 00:04:16,714
Kenapa menatapku seperti itu?

56
00:04:26,391 --> 00:04:27,350
Hei.

57
00:04:28,851 --> 00:04:29,686
Baek-du.

58
00:04:32,689 --> 00:04:34,899
- Aku… 
- Jangan sekarang!

59
00:04:35,984 --> 00:04:38,194
Aku belum mau mendengar jawabanmu.

60
00:04:39,612 --> 00:04:40,947
Kau tak mau dengar?

61
00:04:42,073 --> 00:04:44,575
Lantas kenapa mengatakannya?

62
00:04:44,659 --> 00:04:47,537
Seperti yang kubilang,

63
00:04:47,620 --> 00:04:49,580
aku tak mau ada penyesalan.

64
00:04:50,415 --> 00:04:52,125
Jika aku tak berbuat apa-apa lagi

65
00:04:52,625 --> 00:04:55,086
dan membiarkanmu kembali ke Seoul,

66
00:04:55,670 --> 00:04:57,380
maka kali ini,

67
00:04:57,463 --> 00:05:01,092
bukan hanya penyesalan 20 tahun, 
tapi 200 tahun!

68
00:05:02,719 --> 00:05:05,722
Jadi, biarkan aku bergabung.

69
00:05:06,306 --> 00:05:07,140
Tidak.

70
00:05:08,433 --> 00:05:09,726
Aku akan bergabung.

71
00:05:16,316 --> 00:05:18,818
Astaga, Baek-du, bedebah itu,

72
00:05:19,861 --> 00:05:22,405
selalu membuat jantungku menciut.

73
00:05:22,488 --> 00:05:23,698
HARI INI, AKU AKAN MABUK!

74
00:05:24,449 --> 00:05:26,617
Hatimu akan menciut lebih dahulu.

75
00:05:31,122 --> 00:05:34,000
Astaga, kau akan menyesali ini besok.

76
00:05:34,083 --> 00:05:36,127
Saat kau bangun esok hari…

77
00:05:37,378 --> 00:05:38,629
Astaga.

78
00:05:41,174 --> 00:05:42,425
Hyeon-ja.

79
00:05:42,967 --> 00:05:45,011
Kau pernah memikirkan Du-sik?

80
00:05:46,596 --> 00:05:48,598
Tentu saja pernah.

81
00:05:50,183 --> 00:05:55,521
Dahulu anak-anak selalu bermain bersama.

82
00:05:56,105 --> 00:05:58,441
Aku sesekali memikirkan dia.

83
00:05:59,108 --> 00:06:01,360
Aku memikirkan di mana dia,

84
00:06:01,444 --> 00:06:04,280
bagaimana keadaannya,

85
00:06:04,363 --> 00:06:06,032
dan apakah dia sudah menikah.

86
00:06:07,116 --> 00:06:08,576
Bagaimana denganmu?

87
00:06:10,995 --> 00:06:12,789
Ada sesuatu yang selalu

88
00:06:13,831 --> 00:06:15,249
membebani hatiku.

89
00:06:18,753 --> 00:06:20,421
Du-sik, gadis itu,

90
00:06:21,380 --> 00:06:24,717
sebaya dengan Baek-du, 
tapi jauh lebih cerdas.

91
00:06:25,343 --> 00:06:28,596
Dia terlihat kuat di luar, 
tapi berhati lembut.

92
00:06:28,679 --> 00:06:29,931
Benar.

93
00:06:32,141 --> 00:06:33,684
Dia pasti

94
00:06:35,019 --> 00:06:37,396
sangat terluka saat itu.

95
00:06:44,153 --> 00:06:45,113
Astaga, berhenti.

96
00:06:45,196 --> 00:06:47,824
- Tidak, biar aku saja. 
- Biar kutuangkan.

97
00:06:51,202 --> 00:06:52,912
Mari minum bersama.

98
00:06:59,669 --> 00:07:01,587
Namun, tampaknya orang-orang berubah.

99
00:07:02,171 --> 00:07:04,549
Dahulu aku memikirkannya 100 kali sehari.

100
00:07:05,091 --> 00:07:08,094
Lalu setelah beberapa saat, 
menjadi 50 kali sehari.

101
00:07:09,220 --> 00:07:12,682
Kemudian, setelah lama, 
mungkin kurang dari sepuluh kali.

102
00:07:14,308 --> 00:07:15,601
Lalu suatu hari,

103
00:07:16,269 --> 00:07:19,105
aku bahkan tak memikirkannya.

104
00:07:19,939 --> 00:07:24,068
Aku tahu. Waktu bisa membuat kita lupa.

105
00:07:26,070 --> 00:07:27,572
Begini, anakku Baek-du…

106
00:07:28,990 --> 00:07:32,034
Apa? Kau ini…

107
00:07:32,118 --> 00:07:33,661
Dahulu,

108
00:07:34,620 --> 00:07:37,039
setelah Du-sik pergi seperti itu,

109
00:07:40,001 --> 00:07:43,421
dia menangis selama beberapa hari.

110
00:07:43,963 --> 00:07:46,466
Lalu dia tampak baik-baik saja,

111
00:07:47,300 --> 00:07:52,138
jadi, kukira dia melupakannya. 
Kupikir dia lupa karena masih kecil.

112
00:07:52,680 --> 00:07:55,892
Kau percaya itu?

113
00:08:02,064 --> 00:08:04,358
Aku ibunya,

114
00:08:06,903 --> 00:08:10,364
dan aku tak tahu 
apa yang dilalui putraku sendiri.

115
00:08:11,282 --> 00:08:12,867
Sungguh.

116
00:08:13,951 --> 00:08:16,579
Aku ini ibu terburuk di dunia.

117
00:08:19,749 --> 00:08:21,667
Astaga…

118
00:08:22,668 --> 00:08:25,213
- Jin-suk. 
- Ini membuatku gila.

119
00:08:25,296 --> 00:08:27,298
Kau mabuk berat.

120
00:08:29,717 --> 00:08:32,553
Aku harus mati saja.

121
00:08:32,637 --> 00:08:35,181
- Jangan katakan itu. 
- Astaga.

122
00:08:35,973 --> 00:08:39,685
Apa gunanya hidup?

123
00:08:39,769 --> 00:08:40,686
Ya, ampun.

124
00:08:40,770 --> 00:08:42,063
- Baiklah. 
- Benar, 'kan?

125
00:08:42,146 --> 00:08:43,356
Berhentilah minum.

126
00:08:43,439 --> 00:08:44,273
Suk.

127
00:08:46,150 --> 00:08:48,653
Astaga. Hai.

128
00:08:49,946 --> 00:08:51,239
- Jin-suk. 
- Tunggu.

129
00:08:52,698 --> 00:08:55,368
Aku kenal pria ini.

130
00:08:55,451 --> 00:08:58,037
Kenapa kau minum sebanyak itu?

131
00:08:58,746 --> 00:09:00,831
Pria ini tampak tak asing.

132
00:09:01,874 --> 00:09:03,376
Di mana pernah kulihat?

133
00:09:03,876 --> 00:09:06,337
- Astaga. 
- Aku mabuk.

134
00:09:06,420 --> 00:09:09,590
Begini…

135
00:09:09,674 --> 00:09:11,842
Dia agak sedih hari ini.

136
00:09:11,926 --> 00:09:13,553
Jin-suk.

137
00:09:14,971 --> 00:09:16,806
Begini…

138
00:09:16,889 --> 00:09:19,642
Di depan semua orang, Baek-du berkata

139
00:09:19,725 --> 00:09:21,394
- Du-sik… 
- Aku sudah dengar.

140
00:09:21,477 --> 00:09:22,478
Saat menuju kemari.

141
00:09:22,562 --> 00:09:24,063
Begitu rupanya.

142
00:09:25,606 --> 00:09:28,276
Di mata semua orang,

143
00:09:28,359 --> 00:09:31,112
Baek-du mungkin hanya tampak marah,

144
00:09:31,195 --> 00:09:34,240
tapi ibunya bisa melihat

145
00:09:34,323 --> 00:09:36,867
betapa sedihnya dia.

146
00:09:42,915 --> 00:09:44,208
Hei.

147
00:09:44,834 --> 00:09:46,961
Kim Tae-baek.

148
00:09:50,756 --> 00:09:51,799
Apa?

149
00:09:57,722 --> 00:09:58,639
Apa?

150
00:10:00,600 --> 00:10:04,186
Kita para orang dewasa…

151
00:10:06,230 --> 00:10:08,608
banyak melakukan kesalahan.

152
00:10:10,067 --> 00:10:11,319
Benar, 'kan?

153
00:10:15,156 --> 00:10:16,032
Benar.

154
00:10:18,075 --> 00:10:20,161
Orang dewasa memang banyak salah.

155
00:10:27,126 --> 00:10:30,588
Astaga, aku lelah sekali.

156
00:11:06,248 --> 00:11:07,333
Ayah. Ada apa?

157
00:11:10,670 --> 00:11:11,712
Kau belum tidur.

158
00:11:16,592 --> 00:11:17,843
Ayah mendengar semua.

159
00:11:21,931 --> 00:11:23,766
Begitu rupanya.

160
00:11:26,727 --> 00:11:30,398
Kurasa kabar begitu cepat menyebar.

161
00:11:32,358 --> 00:11:33,818
Cepat sekali.

162
00:11:36,195 --> 00:11:38,364
Itukah alasanmu mengatakannya?

163
00:11:40,199 --> 00:11:41,033
Apa?

164
00:11:43,119 --> 00:11:46,414
Katamu kita tak seharusnya 
biarkan Du-sik pergi seperti itu

165
00:11:48,582 --> 00:11:52,586
dan kita harus melakukan segala cara 
untuk menahannya di sini.

166
00:11:54,797 --> 00:11:56,841
Soal itu…

167
00:11:59,468 --> 00:12:00,428
Baek-du.

168
00:12:02,430 --> 00:12:03,347
Saat itu,

169
00:12:04,348 --> 00:12:05,933
Ayah tak punya pilihan.

170
00:12:07,685 --> 00:12:08,853
Dalam hidup,

171
00:12:09,854 --> 00:12:12,857
ada kalanya ketika kau harus memutuskan.

172
00:12:13,357 --> 00:12:17,611
Dan Ayah tak selalu 
membuat keputusan yang tepat.

173
00:12:19,613 --> 00:12:21,699
Ayah hanya mencari jawaban terbaik

174
00:12:23,451 --> 00:12:25,828
dalam situasi tersebut.

175
00:12:29,081 --> 00:12:30,166
Pada saat itu,

176
00:12:32,126 --> 00:12:33,752
itu pilihan terbaik Ayah.

177
00:12:38,215 --> 00:12:40,009
Namun, hari ini, Ayah sadar

178
00:12:42,136 --> 00:12:43,929
mungkin itu bukan jawaban tepat.

179
00:13:00,404 --> 00:13:01,989
Aku sangat menyukaimu.

180
00:13:03,532 --> 00:13:06,160
Sungguh.

181
00:13:07,536 --> 00:13:11,040
Kau tahu seberapa sering 
aku memikirkan malam itu

182
00:13:11,749 --> 00:13:13,125
dan sebesar apa kusesali itu?

183
00:13:14,293 --> 00:13:15,711
"Seharusnya aku lari lebih cepat."

184
00:13:16,879 --> 00:13:18,756
"Seharusnya kupanggil kau lebih keras."

185
00:13:18,839 --> 00:13:20,799
"Seharusnya aku keluar rumah lebih cepat."

186
00:13:21,342 --> 00:13:24,011
Tidak. "Seharusnya kusadari maksudmu

187
00:13:24,595 --> 00:13:28,516
saat kau datang ke rumahku."

188
00:13:30,059 --> 00:13:32,520
Aku menyesalinya ratusan ribu kali.

189
00:13:33,646 --> 00:13:35,439
Namun, aku tak mau menyesal lagi.

190
00:13:38,317 --> 00:13:40,778
Dahulu aku terlalu kecil

191
00:13:41,946 --> 00:13:45,199
untuk menghentikanmu. 
Aku terpaksa merelakanmu.

192
00:13:45,282 --> 00:13:46,867
Kali ini, tak kubiarkan.

193
00:13:53,916 --> 00:13:55,668
Jadi, biarkan aku bergabung.

194
00:13:56,168 --> 00:13:58,921
Tidak. Aku akan bergabung.

195
00:14:18,691 --> 00:14:20,109
Sial!

196
00:14:21,110 --> 00:14:23,404
Astaga, kalian mengagetkan Ibu!

197
00:14:24,071 --> 00:14:26,282
Kenapa kalian berdiri di sana?

198
00:14:26,365 --> 00:14:29,368
Ibu mengira sedang diculik 
atau semacamnya.

199
00:14:30,369 --> 00:14:32,204
Astaga, kepalaku.

200
00:14:33,414 --> 00:14:37,126
Kepalaku seperti akan meledak.

201
00:14:37,209 --> 00:14:39,295
Kudengar Ibu banyak minum semalam.

202
00:14:39,378 --> 00:14:40,212
Di mana?

203
00:14:42,256 --> 00:14:44,466
Restoran Jin-su. Di mana lagi?

204
00:14:44,550 --> 00:14:46,510
Benar, 'kan? Sudah kubilang.

205
00:14:50,431 --> 00:14:52,266
Astaga, kepalaku sakit.

206
00:14:52,892 --> 00:14:55,811
Pukul berapa Ibu pulang semalam?

207
00:14:59,231 --> 00:15:00,941
Hyeon-ja mengantar Ibu pulang?

208
00:15:01,025 --> 00:15:02,651
Aku selalu merasa

209
00:15:02,735 --> 00:15:05,946
Ibu tak berhak mengomel 
soal kebiasaan minum Baek-du.

210
00:15:06,030 --> 00:15:07,615
Kebiasaan itu jelas dari Ibu.

211
00:15:07,698 --> 00:15:09,408
Hei, minggir.

212
00:15:09,491 --> 00:15:11,452
Menyingkirlah.

213
00:15:12,244 --> 00:15:15,164
Ibu tak boleh mengomelinya 
soal kebiasaan minumnya.

214
00:15:15,247 --> 00:15:16,540
Astaga, kepalaku.

215
00:15:17,666 --> 00:15:19,627
Kenapa? Sesuatu terjadi kemarin?

216
00:15:19,710 --> 00:15:21,962
Ayah menggendong Ibu pulang semalam.

217
00:15:22,046 --> 00:15:23,797
Ayah menempel banyak koyok.

218
00:15:23,881 --> 00:15:26,383
- Benar. 
- Dia pakai di seluruh punggungnya

219
00:15:26,467 --> 00:15:29,511
dan hampir seperti ubin.

220
00:15:29,595 --> 00:15:30,846
Benar.

221
00:15:32,389 --> 00:15:35,726
Omong-omong, saat kami joging pagi tadi,

222
00:15:35,809 --> 00:15:38,437
kami mendengar hal aneh.

223
00:15:38,520 --> 00:15:42,650
Kami mendengar Baek-du bicara 
soal Du-sik di depan banyak orang

224
00:15:42,733 --> 00:15:45,235
dan menjadi sangat marah kemarin. 
Benarkah itu?

225
00:15:52,576 --> 00:15:53,494
Di mana Baek-du?

226
00:15:54,119 --> 00:15:55,496
Dia keluar pagi tadi.

227
00:15:55,579 --> 00:15:57,206
Dia pasti sangat malu.

228
00:15:57,289 --> 00:16:00,167
Semua orang membicarakannya.

229
00:16:03,003 --> 00:16:05,798
Baiklah. Mari lihat.

230
00:16:05,881 --> 00:16:09,718
Aku baru ingat. Baek-du mengamuk kemarin.

231
00:16:09,802 --> 00:16:11,553
Tidak mungkin.

232
00:16:11,637 --> 00:16:13,639
Aku tak pernah melihatnya marah.

233
00:16:13,722 --> 00:16:15,182
Itu juga kali pertamaku.

234
00:16:15,265 --> 00:16:18,435
Katanya kita tak percaya keluarga Du-sik 
dan mengusirnya.

235
00:16:18,519 --> 00:16:19,770
Dia marah sekali.

236
00:16:19,853 --> 00:16:22,314
- Apa? Benarkah? 
- Ya.

237
00:16:22,398 --> 00:16:24,525
Namun, kenapa tiba-tiba bahas Du-sik?

238
00:16:24,608 --> 00:16:26,860
Entahlah. Saat ibunya bertanya

239
00:16:26,944 --> 00:16:29,947
apakah dia memacari Yu-gyeong,

240
00:16:30,030 --> 00:16:32,324
dia tiba-tiba mengamuk.

241
00:16:32,825 --> 00:16:34,284
- Sungguh? 
- Ya.

242
00:16:35,536 --> 00:16:37,121
