00:31:31,848 --> 00:31:33,892
Baek-du, akan kutanya langsung.

498
00:31:36,311 --> 00:31:38,021
Kau menyukai Bu Oh?

499
00:31:40,440 --> 00:31:42,317
Astaga, kalian…

